content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 7905.2 - Compliance with Part 7900 and implementing orders

State Regulations

The provisions of Part 7900 of this subchapter shall be
effective immediately upon the issuance by the Commissioner of the State Energy

Office of an implementing order pursuant to section
7900.2
(b) of this

Subchapter, or upon any other date specified by the commissioner in the
implementing order. Each prime supplier which has been served with an
implementing order shall comply with the provisions of Part 7900 of this
subchapter, and the provisions of any implementing order or order amending an
implementing order issued by the commissioner. Notes
